These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-1::.
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, turtle, bird, horse
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
2. the owner of the turtle is somewhere between the owner of the bird and the owner of the horse##7
3. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Pet   | bird | turtle | horse | guinea-pig |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-2::.
There 4 different types of food: plum, onion, strawberry, eggplant
1. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
2. the person eating strawberry is somewhere between the person eating onion and the person eating plum##7
3. the person eating strawberry is between the person eating onion and the person eating eggplant##2

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Food   | plum | eggplant | strawberry | onion |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-3::.
