.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, taxi, van, skateboard
1. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere between the person driving the van and the person driving the taxi##7
2. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the left of the person driving the skateboard##5
3. the person driving the roller is between the person driving the skateboard and the person driving the van##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |   3   |    4    |
| Transport   | van | roller | skateboard | taxi |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, superhero, scientific, thriller
1. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the person watching superhero movies is between the person watching time-travel movies and the person watching thriller movies##2
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3
4. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere between the person watching scientific movies and the person watching thriller movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |   3   |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | time-travel | superhero | thriller |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: german, canadian, french, pakistani
1. the german is somewhere between the pakistani and the canadian##7
2. the french is somewhere between the german and the pakistani##7
3. the french is on the left or right of the pakistani##3
4. the french is somewhere to the right of the pakistani##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |     3     |    4    |
| Nationality   | pakistani | french | german | canadian |

