1. the person drinking cola is somewhere between the person drinking soy-milk and the person drinking hot-chocolate##7
2. the person drinking sprite is somewhere between the person drinking cola and the person drinking soy-milk##7
3. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |    2     |   3   |      4      |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | cola | sprite | soy-milk |

