2. the person driving the boat is somewhere to the right of the person driving the ship##5
3. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
4. the person driving the boat is somewhere between the person driving the motorbike and the person driving the tram##7

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4    |
| Transport   | tram | ship | boat | motorbike |

